ds.com]] \u2013 Edmunds' Inside Line Editors' Most Wanted Awards: Instant Classic<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.edmunds.com/insideline/do/Features/articleId=135586 |title=2009 Edmunds' Inside Line Editors' Most Wanted Awards |publisher=Edmunds.com |accessdate=July 7, 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090219225704/http://www.edmunds.com/insideline/do/Features/articleId=135586 |archivedate=February 19, 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||''[[Motor Trend]]'' \u2013 Motor Trend Car of the Year<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.motortrend.com/oftheyear/car/112_0901_2009_motor_trend_car_of_the_year_winner_nissan_gt_r/index.html |title=2009 Nissan GT-R \u2013 The 2009 Motor Trend Car of the Year Winner is the Nissan GT-R |publisher=Motor Trend |accessdate=July 7, 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||''[[Popular Science]]'' \u2013 Auto Tech Grand Award Winner<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popsci.com/bown/2008/product/2009-nissan-gt-r |title=2009 Nissan GT-R &#124; Popular Science |publisher=Popsci.com |accessdate=December 19, 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||[[International Car of the Year]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.roadandtravel.com/awards/2009/winners/2009-icoty.htm |title=2009 International Car of the Year Awards' Winners : ROAD & TRAVEL Magazine |publisher=Roadandtravel.com |accessdate=July 7, 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||[[World Car of the Year|World Performance Car]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wcoty.com/media/?release=47&year=2009 |title=World Car of the Year Awards |publisher=wcoty.com |date=April 9, 2009 |accessdate=July 7, 2009}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||[[Targa Tasmania]] Modern Champion\n|-\n|2009||[[Targa West]] Challenge Modern Champion<ref name=TargaWest2009>{{cite web |url=http://www.targawest.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/CHM09_FinalLegResults.pdf |title=Quit Targa West 2009 \u2013 Challenge Modern \u2013 Final Results |publisher=TargaWest |location=Australia |access-date=February 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2009||[[Targa West]] Competition Modern Champion<ref name=Ta